 Ezra Collective 凭借《Where I'm Meant To Be》荣获 2023 年水星奖https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ezra-集体赢得 2023 年水星奖Damian JonesThu, 07 Sep 2023 21:41:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsMercury Prize https://www.nme.com/?p=3494841 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="以斯拉集体" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “对于全国各地为年轻人演奏音乐投入精力和时间的每个组织来说，这是一个特殊的时刻”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">Ezra Collective 凭借《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》荣获 2023 年水星奖后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="以斯拉集体" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>凭借专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-new-album-where-im-meant-to-be-sampa-the-great-life-goes-on-3296522">《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》</a>荣获 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-mercury-prize-interview-nymph-bjork-love-next-album-3474803">Shygirl 接受 Björk、水星奖和她的下一张专辑的建议</a></strong></li></ul><p>今晚（9 月 7 日）在伦敦 Eventim Apollo 举行的颁奖典礼上，这支爵士乐团以局外人的身份击败了最受欢迎的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a>获得了奖项。</p><p> Jamz Supernova 为这群集体颁发了奖项，当他们登上舞台时，他们受到了红色五彩纸屑的欢迎。</p><p>费米·科莱奥索 (Femi Koleoso) 在接受奖杯时说道：“哇，首先让我感谢上帝，因为如果一支爵士乐队赢得水星奖不能让你相信上帝，我不知道还有什么能让你相信上帝。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “我们在这里庆祝的这一刻是对优秀、特别的人的见证。” <a href="https://twitter.com/EzraCollective?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@EzraCollective</a>花点时间向所有有抱负的年轻音乐家大声喊叫，他们与<a href="https://twitter.com/FreeNow_UK?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@FreeNow_UK</a>一起赢得了 2023 年水星奖！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MercuryPrize?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MercuryPrize</a> <a href="https://t.co/IsVXlJs6wI">pic.twitter.com/IsVXlJs6wI</a></p><p> — 水星奖 (@MercuryPrize) <a href="https://twitter.com/MercuryPrize/status/1699906665976303733?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 7 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他接着感谢乐队的经理和他的父母，然后补充道：“Ezra Collective 代表了一些非常特别的东西，因为我们是在一个青年俱乐部认识的。我们所庆祝的是对优秀特别人士的见证，他们为年轻人演奏音乐付出了努力。</p><p> “这不仅仅是 Ezra Collective 和英国爵士乐的成果，对于全国各地为年轻人演奏音乐投入精力和时间的每个组织来说，这都是一个特殊的时刻。”</p><p>乐队早些时候演奏了他们的歌曲《胜利之舞》，并在获奖后第二次表演了这首歌曲。</p><p>当晚，除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a>和目前正在巡演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a>之外，所有艺术家都进行了现场表演。相反，Fred Again.. 在今年的格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演了《Delilah（把我从这一切中拉出来）》，而北极猴子乐队则在<em>稍后节目中表演了《There&#39;d Better Be A Mirrorball》，今年早些时候与 Jools Holland 一起表演了</em>年被放映。 </p><figure id="_0" aria-describedby="caption--0" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/mercury-prize-2023-comp.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption id="caption--0" class="wp-caption-text"> Arctic Monkeys（图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford）、J Hus（图片来源：Burak Cingi/Redferns）和 RAYE（图片来源：Harry Durrant/Getty Images）。</figcaption></figure><p>提名名单上的其他人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> （他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/loyle-carner-hugo-review-an-honest-unflashy-storyteller-3332632">《Hugo》</a>专辑）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/young-fathers-heavy-heavy-review-3389936">《Heavy Heavy》</a> ）、Fred Again..（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fred-again-actual-life-3-review-3336600">《Actual Life 3》（2022 年 1 月 1 日至 9 月 9 日）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> （<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jessie-ware-that-feels-good-album-review-pearls-3434741">《那！感觉很好！&#39;</a> ）。</p><p>该名单还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/raye-my-21st-century-blues-review-3391162#:~:text=Gritty%2C%20honest%20lyrics%2C%20delivered%20by,support%20its%20creator's%20powerhouse%20voice.">《My 21st Century Blues》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hus">J Hus</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/j-hus-beautiful-and-brutal-yard-review-3468251#:~:text=There's%20the%20odd%20lyrical%20blemish,joyous%20return%20from%20J%20Hus.">《Beautiful And Brutal Yard》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a>的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-dean-messy-review-debut-album-radar-3463419">《Messy》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a>的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/shygirl-london-debut-album-review-nymph-radar-3319411">《Nymph》</a> 、Arctic Monkeys 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/arctic-monkeys-the-car-review-3330197">《The Car》</a>和爱尔兰民谣乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lankum">Lankum</a>的第四张唱片“False Lankum”。</p><p> 2023 年水星奖提名专辑完整名单如下：</p><p><strong>北极猴子——“汽车”</strong><br /> <strong>Ezra Collective – “我注定要去的地方”</strong><br /><strong>又是弗雷德.. – 《现实生活 3（2022 年 1 月 1 日至 9 月 9 日）》</strong><br /> <strong>J Hus –《美丽而残酷的院子》</strong><br /><strong>杰西·韦尔——“那个！”感觉不错！&#39;</strong><br /><strong>下体 - “我爱你詹妮弗 B”</strong><br /> <strong>Lankum——“假Lankum”</strong><br /><strong>洛伊尔·卡纳 – “雨果”</strong><br /><strong>奥利维亚·迪恩 – 《凌乱》</strong><br /> <strong>RAYE – “我的 21 世纪布鲁斯”</strong><br /> <strong>Shygirl——“若虫”</strong><br /><strong>年轻的父亲——“Heavy Heavy”</strong></p><p> 2022 年，Little Simz 凭借专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/little-simz-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-review-3035754">《Sometimes I Might Be Introvert》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-wins-the-2022-mercury-prize-for-sometimes-i-might-be-introvert-3331258">获得水星奖</a>。去年十月，这位伦敦说唱歌手击败了其他最受欢迎的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">《自尊》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">《湿腿》</a>的竞争。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">Ezra Collective 凭借《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》荣获 2023 年水星奖后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《Top Boy》在哪里拍摄？主要地点已揭晓https://www.nme.com/news/tv/where-is-top-boy-filmed-main-locations-revealed-3494847?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=where-is-top-boy-filmed-main-地点已揭晓Adam StarkeyThu, 07 Sep 2023 20:50:42 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflixTop Boy https://www.nme.com/?p=3494847 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="顶级男孩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Netflix 节目聚焦伦敦各个地区</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/where-is-top-boy-filmed-main-locations-revealed-3494847">《Top Boy》在哪里拍摄的？透露的主要地点</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="顶级男孩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Top_Boy_Season_5_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/top-boy"><em>《Top Boy》</em></a>在五季之后正式完结。</p><p>这部犯罪剧由罗南·贝内特创作和编剧，讲述了毒贩杜尚（阿什利·沃尔特斯饰）和萨利（凯恩·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kano">卡诺</a>·罗宾逊饰）在伦敦哈克尼虚构的避暑别墅庄园的故事。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/top-boy-review-netflix-3491681">《Top Boy》第五季评论：仍然是 Netflix 上最伟大的电视节目</a></strong></li></ul><p>该剧最初在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/channel-4">Channel 4</a>播出了两季，并于 2013 年停播。随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a> （在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>的帮助下）于 2019 年恢复了<em>《Top Boy》</em> ，第五季也是最后一季是该流媒体服务制作的第三季。</p><p>第五季的其他回归演员包括饰演杜尚搭档雪莱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">小西姆兹</a>、饰演贾克的茉莉花·乔布森和饰演莉兹的丽莎·德万。新加入的成员包括巴里·基奥根和布莱恩·格里森。</p><h2> <em>《Top Boy》</em>在哪里拍摄？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3491125" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491125" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491125" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5.jpg" alt="奥顺雷米" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Araloyin_Oshunremi_Top_Boy_Season_5-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491125" class="wp-caption-text">由于他的兄弟们都去世了，斯特凡扮演了更重要的角色。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>虽然避暑别墅并不真实，但该剧在伦敦使用了多个替身。在第四频道播出的前两季中，庄园内外的外部场景主要在大象堡的海盖特庄园拍摄。</p><p>然而，自从该庄园于 2014 年被拆除以来，《避暑别墅》的许多外部和内部场景都是在狗岛的萨姆达庄园拍摄的。</p><p>哈克尼的波伏瓦庄园被认为是《避暑别墅》的灵感来源，与哈格斯顿、达尔斯顿和纽汉姆等东伦敦地区一起也被用作拍摄地点。</p><p>剧中许多著名的出没地点也是真实存在的，包括第一号咖啡馆（Number One Cafe），它是位于伦敦菲尔兹（London Fields）的一家正常营业的同名咖啡馆。与此同时，Shelley&#39;s Nail Bar 是坎宁镇的一家真正的美甲沙龙，名为 Kiki&#39;s Nail Salon。</p><p>在该剧的第三季中，一些演员还前往牙买加。您可以在下面的拍摄中查看幕后花絮。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">幕后花絮：与<a href="https://twitter.com/micorazonfilms?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@micorazonfilms</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/AshleyWalters82?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@AshleyWalters82</a>在牙买加金斯敦拍摄<a href="https://t.co/AKTGvJ6DVh">pic.twitter.com/AKTGvJ6DVh</a></p><p> - Top Boy (@topboynetflix) <a href="https://twitter.com/topboynetflix/status/1177991609666818051?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2019 年 9 月 28 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最后一季的剧情简介如下：“萨利在上一季结束时的行为改写了他与杜尚的商业规则。随着新的共同问题的出现，他们所建立的一切都受到帝国内外力量的威胁。</p><p> “他们能否按照他们一生所遵循的道路规则在一个正在发生变化的世界中共存？还是只能有一个Top Boy？”</p><p> <em>《Top Boy》</em>可在 Netflix 上观看。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/where-is-top-boy-filmed-main-locations-revealed-3494847">《Top Boy》在哪里拍摄的？透露的主要地点</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
